adams.flow.control.Flow
	-annotation
	The flow loads the UCI dataset \"iris\" and displays \nthe data in a matrix plot.
	-actor
		adams.flow.source.FileSupplier
			-file
			${EXAMPLE_FLOWS}/data/iris.arff
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.WekaFileReader
			-loader
				weka.core.converters.ArffLoader
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.WekaClassSelector
	-actor
		adams.flow.sink.MatrixPlot
			-writer
				adams.gui.print.NullWriter
			-plot-size
			150
			-overlay
				adams.gui.visualization.stats.scatterplot.Lowess
					-line-thickness
					1.0
			-paintlet
				adams.gui.visualization.stats.paintlet.ScatterPaintletCircle
					-stroke-thickness
					0.7
	-flow-execution-listener
		adams.flow.execution.NullListener

